WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.400
 You wish to know about my Grandfather?

2
00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:22.280
 Well, he is nearly 93 years old, yet he still thinks as swiftly as ever.

3
00:00:27.180 --> 00:00:36.320
 He addresses himself in an old black frock coat, usually several buttons are missing.

4
00:00:42.080 --> 00:00:53.160
 A long beard clings to his chin, giving those who observe him renounced feeling of the utmost respect.

5
00:00:57.380 --> 00:01:09.160
 When he speaks, his voice is just a bit cracked and quivers a bit.

6
00:01:12.780 --> 00:01:19.560
 Twice each day, he plays skillfully and with a jest upon a small organ.

7
00:01:28.120 --> 00:01:38.040
 Except in the winter, when the snow or ice prevents, he slowly takes a short walk in the open air each day.

8
00:01:42.460 --> 00:01:54.620
 We have often urged him to walk more and smoke less, but he always answers banana oil.

9
00:01:58.480 --> 00:02:02.040
 Grandfather likes to be modern in his language.

